INSERT INTO `gre` VALUES ('relapse', '[rɪ\'læps]', 'v.复发；再陷入；故态复萌 n.再发；重陷；故态复萌', '1. Some patients will relapse. 一些患者会复发。 2. We were afraid he might relapse into a coma. 我们担心他可能再次陷入昏迷。 3. He had relapsed into silence again. 他再一次陷入沉默。 4. He kept off drink for a few weeks, but now he has relapsed. 他酒戒了两三个星期，可是现在故态复萌。 5. He can\'t return to work because he\'s had a relapse. 他不能回去工作，因为旧病复发了。', '名词: relapser 过去式: relapsed 过去分词: relapsed 现在分词: relapsing 第三人称单数: relapses');
INSERT INTO `gre` VALUES ('genus', '[\'dʒiːnəs]', 'n.[生物学]属；<口>类；种；型', '1. The daffodil belongs to the genus Narcissus. 黄水仙是水仙属植物。 2. Dogs, wolves, and coyotes belong to the same genus. 狗、狼和土狼是同属。 3. That genus of plants differentiates into three species. 那个属种的植物衍生出三个变种。', '名词复数: genera');
