INSERT INTO `gre` VALUES ('gutter', '[\'ɡʌtər]', 'n.排水沟；槽；贫民区 vi.形成沟；淌蜡；(蜡烛)忽明忽暗 vt.开沟于', '1. There\'s a cigarette packet thrown into the gutter. 阴沟里有个香烟盒。 2. The workers are dishing a gutter. 工人们在挖沟。 3. The motorbike lay on its side in the gutter. 那辆摩托车倒在沟中。 4. The heavy rain has filled up the gutter again. 大雨又把水槽填满了。 5. The candle was guttering in the candlestick. 蜡烛在烛台上淌着蜡。', '过去式: guttered 过去分词: guttered 现在分词: guttering 第三人称单数: gutters');
